The evidence with the title 'Did Nancy Pelosi say obamacare must be passed to 'find out what ... ' says Oct 17, 2017  ... A much - reproduced quote from the former speaker of the House about the passage of the Affordable Care Act is typically presented out of context. 16K. CLAIM . House minority leader Nancy Pelosi said of the Affordable Care Act, in 2010 : "we have to pass the bill so that you can find out what is in it.". 
